Third Department,

April, 1956

(April 4, 1956) In the Matter of the Claim of Irving Cohen, Appellant, against Tide Water Associated Oil Co. et al., Respondents. Workmen’s Compensation Board, Respondent.

Motion for permission to withdraw appeal granted, without costs. Present — Foster, P. J., Bergan, Coon, Halpern and Gibson, JJ.
